To run GWT unit tests in the IDE, it's necessary to increase the VM memory size for unit tests. 

i.e. -Xmx512M -XX:MaxPermSize=128M

# Eclipse #

In the test class: Right Click > Run Configurarions... > go to "Arguments" tab > set it under "VM Arguments"

# Servlet #

The user must add Guice listener, filter and filter mapping in web.xml. 

sample: https://github.com/ArcBees/ArcBees-tools/blob/master/archetypes/gwtp-appengine-objectify/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/web.xml